Converts a `Path` to a [`Cow<str>`](../borrow/enum.Cow.html "enum std::borrow::Cow").

Any non-Unicode sequences are replaced with [`U+FFFD REPLACEMENT CHARACTER`](../char/constant.REPLACEMENT_CHARACTER.html "constant std::char::REPLACEMENT_CHARACTER").

##### [Â§](#examples-13)Examples

Calling `to_string_lossy` on a `Path` with valid unicode:

```
