Returns `true` if the path points at an existing entity.

Warning: this method may be error-prone, consider using [`try_exists()`](about:blank/struct.Path.html#method.try_exists "method std::path::Path::try_exists") instead! It also has a risk of introducing time-of-check to time-of-use (TOCTOU) bugs.

This function will traverse symbolic links to query information about the destination file.

